        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "When creating optgroups, the label is also used as part of the id:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n$opt_id = ' id=\"' . $this->view->escape($id) . '-optgroup-'\r\n        . $this->view->escape($opt_value) . '\"';\r\n\r\n$list[] = '<optgroup'\r\n        . $opt_disable\r\n        . $opt_id\r\n        . ' label=\"' . $this->view->escape($opt_value) .'\">';\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nThis breaks when the label contains spaces or html entities, e.g. \r\n\"Waren &amp; Fremdleistungen\", both spaces and & are not allowed in ids.\r\n"
        },
