                    "body": "Code tags added.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=frosch",
                        "name": "frosch",
                        "displayName": "Frank Br\u00fcckner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-02-10T07:30:02.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-02-10T07:30:02.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/49774",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=adamlundrigan",
                        "name": "adamlundrigan",
                        "displayName": "Adam Lundrigan",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Confirmed.  Label value is not filtered before being used in the optgroup id.\r\n{code}\r\n1) Zend_View_Helper_FormSelectTest::testHtml4OptGroupLabelIsProperlySantiziedBeforeUseInId\r\n<select name=\"baz\" id=\"baz\">\r\n    <optgroup id=\"baz-optgroup-Foo &amp;&amp; BAR\" label=\"Foo &amp;&amp; BAR\">\r\n    <option value=\"1\" label=\"one\">one<\/option>\r\n    <option value=\"2\" label=\"two\">two<\/option>\r\n    <\/optgroup>\r\n<\/select>\r\nFailed asserting that <text> matches PCRE pattern \"\/<optgroup[^>]*?id=\"baz-optgroup-FooBAR\"[^>]*?\/\".\r\n\r\ntests\/Zend\/View\/Helper\/FormSelectTest.php:347\r\n\r\n2) Zend_View_Helper_FormSelectTest::testHtml5OptGroupLabelIsProperlySantiziedBeforeUseInId\r\n<select name=\"baz\" id=\"baz\">\r\n    <optgroup id=\"baz-optgroup-Foo &amp;&amp; BAR\" label=\"Foo &amp;&amp; BAR\">\r\n    <option value=\"1\" label=\"one\">one<\/option>\r\n    <option value=\"2\" label=\"two\">two<\/option>\r\n    <\/optgroup>\r\n<\/select>\r\nFailed asserting that <text> matches PCRE pattern \"\/<optgroup[^>]*?id=\"baz-optgroup-Foo&&BAR\"[^>]*?\/\".\r\n\r\ntests\/Zend\/View\/Helper\/FormSelectTest.php:365\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nAttached patch which corrects this behavior, according to id element rules found here: http:\/\/stackoverflow.com\/a\/79022",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=adamlundrigan",
                        "name": "adamlundrigan",
                        "displayName": "Adam Lundrigan",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-02-25T17:23:12.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-02-25T17:23:12.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/49775",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=adamlundrigan",
                        "name": "adamlundrigan",
                        "displayName": "Adam Lundrigan",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "One thing to note is that the label value is escaped before being used in the id, which means  {{& -> &amp;amp;}}.  Not sure if this is the intended behavior. ",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=adamlundrigan",
                        "name": "adamlundrigan",
                        "displayName": "Adam Lundrigan",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-02-25T17:26:55.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-02-25T17:27:27.000+0000"
                }
            ]
